---
title: Veggie Black Bean and Mushroom 'Meatballs' with Tomato Sauce
description: Savoury mushrooms and mashed black beans combine for a meatball experience like no other! The rich tomato ragu is the perfect bed for these luxurious veggie meatballs, topped off herbaceous parsley and served with toasty garlic bread for a restaurant-worthy finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/veggie-black-bean-and-mushroom-meatballs-4bdb34ab.jpg
